|        2 | Bob           | Phone        | 2025-08-06 14:10:00 |        2 | 650.50 | pending | 456 Elm St, LA      |
|        6 | Fiona         | Mouse        | 2025-08-04 10:30:00 |        4 |  25.00 | shipped | 321 Oak St, Houston |
