18. Write a query to show all customer names in uppercase.
mysql> select upper(username) as uppercase_username from users;
+--------------------+
| uppercase_username |
+--------------------+
| ALICE123           |
| BOB99              |
| CHARLIEX           |
| DANA_88            |
| ELI                |
| FAY                |
| GINA007            |
+--------------------+
